{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"content_hash":"28d9bf5872a85c4907fd325461e3f0eda31a5d766d876321fc61f5d1797d3222","digest":{"component_or_area":"identity authenticated-authorship enforcement gate","key_entities":["identity.require_authenticated","enforce_since","rebar.toml","8dcef776c3dd9e68935b74b82137e1ffd8f04f10","rebar verify-identity","finalize_event","author_sig","REBAR_IDENTITY_REQUIRE_AUTHENTICATED","test_enrich_drain_prune_concurrency.py","_prune_race_worker.py","reconcile-bridge","Gerrit change 759","authorship_ledger"],"problem_keywords":["enforcement flip","authenticated authorship","unsigned events","merge-gate","grandfathering","write-gate","multi-agent shared store","rollback","pre-flip validation","atomic config change"],"propositions":["Flip identity.require_authenticated=true and pin enforce_since to the 8d91 anchor SHA in a single atomic rebar.toml change.","A pre-flip gate must prove no active writer emits unsigned non-SNAPSHOT in-scope events before enabling enforcement, since concurrent agents on old pre-0ba4 worktree builds still write unsigned txn events.","Enforcement must be demonstrated as real (not advisory): verify-identity exits non-zero on forged/unsigned post-boundary events and the local write-gate refuses unsignable writes with the signing key unset.","Every in-scope writer surface (local, CI reconcile-bridge, Gerrit review-bot LINK) must sign and verify under enforcement without pushing red on main.","A documented single-change rollback path must exist to set require_authenticated=false if a writer surface unexpectedly fails post-flip.","The enrich-drain prune concurrency test broke under enforcement because its subprocess writers had no signing configured, requiring it to run enforcement-agnostic."]},"digest_hash_version":1,"model":"claude-opus-4-8","schema":"ticket_digest_v1"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"TICKET_DIGEST","timestamp":1784263237399519001,"uuid":"ebab729e-b4df-488c-91fa-946d714e2896"}